{"tid":1525706,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【警察會呃你話唔得】其實除左我無嘢講, 仲可以事後用書面形式去答警察嘅提問。","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T18:17:36.000Z","uid":273854,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cdebf3890378dae81bb7b3d7c6f0ead9a54311","tid":1525706,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:26:18.000Z","msg":"被拘捕至保釋前<br />\n答『我無嘢講』相信大家都已經記熟<br />\n有需要記得要好好運用<br />\n<br />\n但相信有人會覺得自己真係無辜<br />\n又或者真係好想解釋<br />\n(有律師都提過, 一直答我無嘢講, 有機會增加legal cost)<br />\n其實有一個幾安全嘅方法<br />\n就係事後用書面解釋<br />\n(當然係比律師睇過先啦)<br />\n<br />\n有一點可以證明<br />\n咁做係對被人捕人有利<br />\n而對警方極不利<br />\n就係警方一定同你講『唔可以』<br />\n『我地唔會接受你書面嘅答案』<br />\n點解會話唔得?<br />\n因為對警方係好不利<br />\n<br />\n但明明警察話唔得, 咁仲係唔係有用??<br />\n答案係100% 有用<br />\n有無用, 唔係警察說了就算<br />\n而係法庭會唔會接納<br />\n至於警察話唔接受, 點樣迫佢地接受呢?<br />\n最底下會講<br />\n<br />\n直接入正題。<br />\n如果大家真係想書面回答問題<br />\n(強調, 啲答案要比律師過目先)<br />\n有兩個方法:<br />\n1. 陳述書形式<br />\n即係你自己好似作文咁, 講返事發經過<br />\n例如:<br />\n我係陳大文, 香港身份證號碼......<br />\n係幾時幾時, 我係邊度做過啲乜.....<br />\n2. 就住警察問嘅問題, 遂條回答<br />\n即係當時警察問咗10條問題, 你就答返10條問題。<br />\n<br />\n好喇<br />\n咁警察明明話唔接受<br />\n咁你可以點比佢呢?<br />\n就係用掛號信<br />\n<br />\n用掛號信, 警察無得唔簽收<br />\n(相反, 如果警察唔簽收, 郵局張回條會證明到佢地拒絕你合法解釋)<br />\n<br />\n咁會點幫到呢?<br />\n其實警察口講就話唔接受<br />\n但實際佢地都會你用書面回答係有法律效力<br />\n所以如果你嘅書面回答真係解釋到你係無辜<br />\n警察係唔可以當睇唔到, 亂告你上法庭<br />\n否則到時上法庭<br />\n可以比辯方用惡意檢控為由<br />\n申請永久終止審訊, 同埋向警察民事追討賠償<br />\n<br />\n但再次強調<br />\n無論以任何書面形式去回答問題<br />\n都一定要經律師過目<br />\n(事實上, 現行做刑事嘅古惑老手律師, 都會用呢個方法去答問題)<br />\n而且你要衡量過<br />\n如果你乜都唔答<br />\n會對自己有利<br />\n(乜都唔答, 警察會唔夠證據告上法庭)<br />\n定對自己不利呢<br />\n(乜都唔答, 警察夠表證可以將你告上法庭)"},{"pid":"7643122c90e9a05329e7caade3a65e0bba1659d4","tid":1525706,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:26:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"062b76b86c3eebe8b5f56473a845e475fbbc97a2","tid":1525706,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"未聽過書面回覆<br />\n又真係好似好有道理<br />\n無得唔接受"},{"pid":"87980beda60de7f71d2ad7cd755a5d24778514c7","tid":1525706,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"好似有d料度"},{"pid":"91319bb7a15e0b29998b9f45f9e0930a9b05dc4f","tid":1525706,"uid":273854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062b76b86c3eebe8b5f56473a845e475fbbc97a2","tid":1525706,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"未聽過書面回覆<br />\n又真係好似好有道理<br />\n無得唔接受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"有古惑大律師會教client咁做<br />\n當然大律師們係知<br />\n如果client 唔答嘢<br />\n警察會因為有足夠表證而告上法庭<br />\n咁嘅情況下<br />\n只係遲早嘅嘅分別<br />\n佢client 到時一樣要係法庭上作出答辯<br />\n<br />\n但又係留意返<br />\n你確信你真係無辜先好咁做<br />\n否則就算係書面<br />\n一樣有機會講錯嘢指證返自己<br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n例如你真係岩岩地鐵落車<br />\n唔知站外驅散緊人群<br />\n你一步出地鐵站<br />\n就比警察拉咗<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況下<br />\n如果你一直『我無嘢講』<br />\n警察係會將你告上法庭<br />\n到時你一樣要係法庭上申辯<br />\n<br />\n但如果你真係有向警方解釋過<br />\n而警方對你嘅解釋唔能夠搵出合理反駁<br />\n(舉證責任在控方)<br />\n(被捕人唔駛主動拎記錄證明自己講嘅係事實, 除非你嘅故事係好特別, 一般人都覺得唔合理唔可信)<br />\n(警方如果唔接納你嘅解釋, 警方要搵到一個合理說法, 話你嘅解釋唔可信, 例如站內cctv 影到你唔係岩岩落車)<br />\n就唔可以輕易告你上法庭<br />\n當然佢打橫嚟都可以, 但一來律政司唔會肯(律政司入面比指引嘅律師, 有機會比人去律師公會投訴)。<br />\n而且警察自己都會計算過, 對佢有害無利。明知亂告你上法庭, 法庭會接受你個辯解, 結果佢只會比法官鬧, 仲有機會比被捕人告返轉頭。"},{"pid":"4fc73698c0516e07f1e399c7cfeab398c69b5307","tid":1525706,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZ8JRV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmZ8JRV.gif&h=d48b36ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e1cdc0aaf2bcdaf8053016f339d9371923b71d","tid":1525706,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2327248eafad64cc1ea9ef42b0158a606fc5f286","tid":1525706,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ec191935cceee5f7bfb24dce6082f52aed43861","tid":1525706,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9daf3fcbd6df91981f21f0f6845f2ba52fa9b4ae","tid":1525706,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n遲到好果無到教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3fedfc75a45e43c11d44c5569c7d6f74b1cb75c","tid":1525706,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"推到前線手足見倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62764a3a145c872f471d5f709eedd1d12a21af5e","tid":1525706,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21f4bfdd2f8dd40a423ae367c54a8c979a882a03","tid":1525706,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb5ae32e7fc998c25080feeef04d36621c592855","tid":1525706,"uid":149225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed1073d2a08984e09359238001542f33fdb2e826","tid":1525706,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1395cfd7ffb77d1be4c5e9080710b8b47f9b3ff0","tid":1525706,"uid":141686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e9154570cf2673dfe9e2bba34f0c0c78d605e4c3","tid":1525706,"uid":141686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b278cb16ced5f2cadb6d09b39f1ff078d5b2834","tid":1525706,"uid":70332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"511ffcbcf873490576744eb95d842f9ce1fa1107","tid":1525706,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"有無真法律巴打fc下"},{"pid":"7a49aef5ed39867d010f472b1007fe960ba75798","tid":1525706,"uid":122185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"和理非，好無力，好忟？<br />\n要抗爭，只有十月一前每日堅持做以下既事，係堅持，堅唔到都要堅，係呢到發誓你堅持呢個九月，就一個月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 罷消費（任何福建幫、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、藍紅食店）好難？勇武難唔難？<br />\n2. 低享樂（要發洩，做運動、十點9叫、唔好taobao消費食好野）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 每日like and share 1個文宣post<br />\n5. 下載Twitter 開acc,每日出1個post<br />\n6. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n8. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n11. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"760f093e7143a2b17d61317e23463c610a801612","tid":1525706,"uid":285118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"有無法律巴絲"},{"pid":"e46b62a5dac4a1e5b639ac6fdcf9885b08fd20a2","tid":1525706,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"搵人理下我 ，支持請留名721 831<br />\n<br />\n《千萬唔好》打爆所有警察出現既地鐵站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529094</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}